  |<b><color:red>PK</color></b> = Primary Key|
  |<i><color:blue>FK</color></i> = Foreign Key|
  |**Cardinality:**|
  ||| = One (1)|
  |o{ = Many (0..*)|
  |-- = Relationship|
endlegend

@enduml

